and it might not seem fair but...

41:05.862 --> 41:07.896
<i>Fair? You're talking about fair.</i>

41:07.898 --> 41:11.032
<i>What's not fair is that chickens
spend their whole life in cages</i>

41:11.034 --> 41:14.235
