Alprazolam, some kind of...

41:53.577 --> 41:56.213
Oh, look, empty already.
Good for you.

41:58.047 --> 42:02.083
Okay. Deep breath.
You're mad.

42:02.085 --> 42:03.985
I get it. You're mad.

42:03.987 --> 42:06.920
Do you have any idea
how disgusting it is

42:06.922 --> 42:10.090
