walked in on you beating off?

42:10.092 --> 42:11.828
Any idea?

42:12.929 --> 42:14.999
[soft music over headphones]

42:29.012 --> 42:30.748
[slow music]

42:33.382 --> 42:35.919
[Karen speaking indistinctly]

42:38.088 --> 42:42.927
Where are my keys?
Who took my keys?

42:43.927 --> 42:46.293
Everyone take my things
and they never put them back!

42:46.295 --> 42:49.697
- All right. Just...
- No one respects anything of mine.

42:49.699 --> 42:51.668
Just take a breath, okay.

42:52.702 --> 42:55.802
I can't breathe.
I do everything for this family,

42:55.804 --> 42:58.271
I do it all.
I sit at fucking ice rinks

42:58.273 --> 43:01.208
