- Okay.

44:12.782 --> 44:14.218
Oh.

44:19.088 --> 44:21.054
Oh...

44:21.056 --> 44:22.959
[tension music]

44:28.097 --> 44:31.134
[moaning]

44:46.782 --> 44:48.483
- Oh, my God.
- I'm fine.

44:48.485 --> 44:51.918
- I'm fine.
- Dad! You're bleeding.

44:51.920 --> 44:54.155
- No, I'm...
- Oh, my God. There's so much blood.

44:54.157 --> 44:56.791
- I'm calling 911.
- No. We're not calling 911.

44:56.793 --> 44:58.325
Yes, you are going
to the hospital.

44:58.327 --> 45:00.128
- I can't go to the hospital.
- It's everywhere.

45:00.130 --> 45:02.130
No, no. It's fine.
I'm fine. I'm fine.

45:02.132 --> 45:04.134
I'm calling 911.
I'm getting you ice, okay.

45:05.300 --> 45:07.068
Why the hell is the ice
in this house?

45:07.070 --> 45:08.836
Calm down.
The kids will hear you.

45:08.838 --> 45:10.972
It looks and feels
worse than it is.

45:10.974 --> 45:12.807
You want me to calm
down when my father's dying?

45:12.809 --> 45:14.175
- I'm not dying.
- Put this on your face.

45:14.177 --> 45:16.010
- Oh.
- Watch it. I'm sorry.

45:16.012 --> 45:17.979
Did she do this to you?
if she did,

45:17.981 --> 45:20.014
- this is attempted murder.
- It's an accident.

45:20.016 --> 45:22.385
- It's an accident.
- How is it an accident?

45:24.920 --> 45:27.390
- It's fine. We're fine.
- Oh, my God.

45:28.291 --> 45:31.391
If I lost my job, he'll be
the first person I told.

45:31.393 --> 45:35.463
I would've told him and...
how can he not tell me?

45:35.465 --> 45:37.063
Stop eating that.

45:37.065 --> 45:38.132
You're not even listening to me.

45:38.134 --> 45:40.501
I am, but you can say it

45:40.503 --> 45:43.170
- without stuffing your face.
- What?

45:43.172 --> 45:45.173
If you're going to be back
on the market again,

45:45.175 --> 45:46.243
you got to stay in shape.

45:46.976 --> 45:48.342
You wanted this to happen.

45:48.344 --> 45:50.378
Don't be ridiculous.

45:50.380 --> 45:53.046
I stopped wishing
for this years ago.

45:53.048 --> 45:54.884
Oh.

46:05.894 --> 46:06.764
[soft music]

46:09.032 --> 46:12.967
- [knocking]
- [mother] Honey! Honey, open the door.

46:12.969 --> 46:14.438
It was just a joke.

46:25.581 --> 46:27.049
Are you guys getting a divorce?

46:28.117 --> 46:29.920
What? No, no.

46:33.056 --> 46:33.956
Good night, dad.

46:35.023 --> 46:37.527
[soft music continues]

47:02.085 --> 47:05.389
[Henry]
Lights on. Lights off.

47:07.456 --> 47:08.991
Lights on.

47:10.994 --> 47:11.995
Lights off.

47:14.197 --> 47:15.833
Lights on.

47:16.965 --> 47:20.269
Lights off. Lights on.

47:24.039 --> 47:26.139
[soft music continues]

47:26.141 --> 47:28.110
[phone ringing]

47:39.054 --> 47:42.523
- Hello.
- [Travis] <i>Mrs. Warner, this is Travis Parker.</i>

47:42.525 --> 47:44.925
<i>I spoke to you once before
and it's really important</i>

47:44.927 --> 47:47.327
- <i>that I talk to your husband.</i>
- Travis?

47:47.329 --> 47:49.195
How did you get this number?

47:49.197 --> 47:50.398
Your daughter gave it to me.

47:50.400 --> 47:52.001
Well, of course she did.

47:53.001 --> 47:57.338
[sighs] Travis, right now
I'm smoking a joint

47:57.340 --> 47:59.273
and my husband isn't here so...

47:59.275 --> 48:01.575
<i>I used to wake and bake.</i>

48:01.577 --> 48:05.179
<i>I can't smoke weed anymore, it
makes me a little bit paranoid.</i>

48:05.181 --> 48:09.115
Travis, I just got my period

48:09.117 --> 48:10.485
and I'm having
really bad cramps.

48:11.954 --> 48:16.090
I just found out two hours ago that
my husband is lying to me so...

48:16.092 --> 48:18.394
Yeah, it's a little weird.
I guess I knew before you.

48:19.594 --> 48:21.430
Apparently, I'm the only one
that didn't know.

48:38.981 --> 48:39.682
[moaning]

48:54.764 --> 48:56.066
[burps]

49:01.637 --> 49:03.371
You need to take us to school.

49:03.373 --> 49:05.206
- [phone ringing]
- What?

49:05.208 --> 49:07.041
You need to take us to school.

49:07.043 --> 49:08.275
I know. Let's go.

49:08.277 --> 49:10.276
We didn't have breakfast.

49:10.278 --> 49:12.146
We'll stop at Dunkin Donuts.

49:12.148 --> 49:15.085
[phone continues ringing]

49:16.619 --> 49:18.322
[grunts] God.

49:21.023 --> 49:23.289
Wait till he disconnects
the cellphone.

49:23.291 --> 49:25.628
[Travis grunts] Shit.

49:42.545 --> 49:43.447
[slow music]

50:06.702 --> 50:08.138
Please, please... [cries]

50:10.639 --> 50:14.377
I want you to come home... now.

50:15.811 --> 50:18.347
- I will.
- <i>I love you.</i>

50:19.181 --> 50:22.785
I just have to help nana out
for a couple more days, okay?

50:23.652 --> 50:27.088
I miss you. Please, come home.

50:27.090 --> 50:31.495
Hey, is that mommy?
Here, let me talk. Karen.

50:34.563 --> 50:36.199
[slow music continues]

50:39.601 --> 50:41.469
[phone ringing]

50:41.471 --> 50:43.340
[grunts]

50:53.215 --> 50:55.518
Wow. Look at you.

50:57.320 --> 50:58.188
I know.

50:59.889 --> 51:04.557
- I'm turning 70 next month.
- Congratulations.

51:04.559 --> 51:06.392
- Fuck you.
- Oh.

51:06.394 --> 51:08.097
Twenty five years.

51:09.164 --> 51:12.532
Twenty five fucking years
of chasing down junkies,

51:12.534 --> 51:15.836
