out of lying assholes

51:15.838 --> 51:18.175
and now I'm getting squeezed
out of this shithole.

51:19.775 --> 51:20.644
You know what?

51:21.911 --> 51:23.443
That's fine.

51:23.445 --> 51:25.679
It's real fucking fine.

51:25.681 --> 51:28.617
And you know why?
Because I'm free.

51:29.619 --> 51:34.091
And you guys... you guys
are still stuck in this shit.

51:35.757 --> 51:38.394
Don't say I didn't tell you.

51:40.262 --> 51:42.264
- [door shuts]
- He didn't close.

52:01.851 --> 52:05.586
[laughs] I envy you,
no really I do.

52:05.588 --> 52:09.956
You probably don't have
any idea how good you got it.

52:09.958 --> 52:11.758
Mr. Warner,
you need to listen to me.

52:11.760 --> 52:13.427
<i>Go anywhere you want,</i>

52:13.429 --> 52:15.132
have sex with anyone you want.

52:16.199 --> 52:22.202
Oh, Travis... I don't even
remember the last time I had sex.

52:22.204 --> 52:24.771
<i>Mr. Warner, that doesn't matter.
Unless you pay your bills,</i>

52:24.773 --> 52:27.907
they're going to take away
your house, repo all your cars.

52:27.909 --> 52:30.311
Your credit will be so fucked,
you won't be able to open

52:30.313 --> 52:32.713
a cellphone account, okay?
And top of that,

52:32.715 --> 52:34.847
guess what, your family's going to
be living on the fucking streets,

52:34.849 --> 52:35.851
do you really want that?

52:36.952 --> 52:39.286
I lost my job, Travis.

52:39.288 --> 52:40.856
I didn't even tell my wife.

52:41.958 --> 52:43.726
I... I don't know.

52:44.726 --> 52:47.830
I guess I thought everything
was going to work out somehow.

52:48.597 --> 52:49.833
I didn't want them to worry.

52:51.099 --> 52:54.668
[sighs] I didn't want them to
worry because I'm supposed to be

52:54.670 --> 52:56.336
the guy who takes care
of things like that.

52:56.338 --> 52:57.773
It's my job to protect them,

52:58.873 --> 53:00.176
so I didn't tell them.

53:01.911 --> 53:03.380
Dumbest thing I could have done

53:04.512 --> 53:06.679
- and I did it.
- <i>Mr. Warner,</i>

53:06.681 --> 53:08.916
unless you want your daughters
to become washed-up strippers

53:08.918 --> 53:09.983
banging dudes for food stamps...

53:09.985 --> 53:11.885
I'm back here... Matty...

53:11.887 --> 53:13.720
I suggest you get
a new fucking job...

53:13.722 --> 53:15.356
