53:15.358 --> 53:16.893
You haven't even fucking tried!

53:17.994 --> 53:20.026
Matty, come back here.

53:20.028 --> 53:21.463
Sorry.

53:24.400 --> 53:26.700
- [Henry] All I asked was that you watch them.
- I was watching them.

53:26.702 --> 53:29.869
You weren't, if you were,
this would not have happened.

53:29.871 --> 53:32.706
