of them every second, dad.

53:32.708 --> 53:34.974
- Can you not argue with me, please?
- Stop fighting.

53:34.976 --> 53:36.342
- We're not fighting.
- Stop.

53:36.344 --> 53:37.945
I don't want to fight

53:37.947 --> 53:39.746
if we could just be quiet
and let me think.

53:39.748 --> 53:41.414
- [Trinity] You want this?
- [Henry] No.

53:41.416 --> 53:43.516
You're going to have to grow up

53:43.518 --> 53:45.688
stop making excuses
and take some responsibility.

53:47.389 --> 53:51.560
Like what? Losing your job
and not telling anybody?

53:54.030 --> 53:57.563
You were living on fumes
and you didn't even know it.

53:57.565 --> 53:59.967
You have to have
your own money.

53:59.969 --> 54:04.003
- You can never count on...
- Someone else to do that for you, I know,

54:04.005 --> 54:06.706
and I have been working,
so this is not helping me.

54:06.708 --> 54:09.043
Plus, you're not having sex.

54:09.045 --> 54:11.644
Why don't you just
tell everyone at the bar?

54:11.646 --> 54:14.750
Oh, you can't see
how fucked up your life is.

54:18.320 --> 54:21.257
The guy at the other end
of the bar sent these over.

54:23.793 --> 54:29.362
Mm-hmm. Well, thanks.
[laughs]

54:29.364 --> 54:33.969
If he's looking for cougars,
he can bag this big old cat. Hm.

54:36.838 --> 54:42.675
[man on the TV] <i>Known as Vlad the Impaler after
his chosen means of execution and torture,</i>

54:42.677 --> 54:48.984
<i>Dracula had boiled, burned, and
dismembered his way into the history books.</i>

55:01.864 --> 55:02.898
Yes.

55:10.039 --> 55:11.007
Yes.

55:16.378 --> 55:17.880
Yes!

55:21.951 --> 55:23.385
[sighs] Okay.

55:35.030 --> 55:36.032
I'm sorry.

55:37.599 --> 55:41.534
- Don't worry about it.
- I overreacted, sweetheart.

55:41.536 --> 55:43.970
You were right about me and I
was wrong and we're frustrated...

55:43.972 --> 55:49.008
Dad, it's okay.
