55:49.010 --> 55:51.380
Here. Have these
before they get cold.

55:56.152 --> 55:59.519
What? Is this tofu?
I don't like tofu.

55:59.521 --> 56:02.088
- It's not tofu.
- [Henry] Did she poison it?

56:02.090 --> 56:03.826
[Trinity] No.

56:04.460 --> 56:05.992
All right.
No, I'm going to eat this.

56:05.994 --> 56:09.028
By the way, you have
a job interview today.

56:09.030 --> 56:10.132
No. No, I don't.

56:11.967 --> 56:12.836
Dad.

56:18.907 --> 56:19.909
Check your email.

56:23.913 --> 56:28.916
[woman over radio] ...traffic?
Not that is too bad either...

56:28.918 --> 56:30.686
[mother moans]

56:36.025 --> 56:37.594
I hope you use protection.

56:37.992 --> 56:38.927
Are you kidding?

56:40.094 --> 56:43.165
At my age you just pray
you don't get cervical cancer.

56:45.900 --> 56:46.969
[moans]

56:57.679 --> 57:03.851
[woman] <i>Is there a reason your
resume says you are 25 years old?</i>

57:03.853 --> 57:08.758
<i>I don't appreciate people
wasting my time, Mr. Warner.</i>

57:12.126 --> 57:13.061
<i>Fuck.</i>

57:20.068 --> 57:21.869
I got you the interview,
it's your job to do the rest.

57:21.871 --> 57:24.237
- You can't lie to people.
- You lie to people.

57:24.239 --> 57:27.139
Yep, look what that got me in.
You shouldn't drink coffee...

57:27.141 --> 57:29.575
You are drinking coffee
right now.

57:29.577 --> 57:31.744
- It's not helpful.
- I am like a free therapist...

57:31.746 --> 57:33.981
- I don't need...
- [man] Henry.

57:33.983 --> 57:36.950
- Scott. Hey, man.
- Hey, man.

57:36.952 --> 57:38.818
You're looking good.
Did you lose some weight?

57:38.820 --> 57:40.153
Just rocking
the stress diet.

57:40.155 --> 57:41.858
Is this your wife?

57:42.557 --> 57:45.224
- Father. That's my father.
- Daughter. That's my daughter.

57:45.226 --> 57:47.293
[speaks in a foreign language]

57:47.295 --> 57:49.963
- What?
- Hello, pretty young lady.

57:49.965 --> 57:52.199
- Right.
- You probably don't know this,

57:52.201 --> 57:55.601
but your dad
was a rockstar at work.

57:55.603 --> 57:58.005
Wow. Dad, you never
tell me these things.

57:58.007 --> 58:00.139
Ah, well, you know, sometimes
I don't tell you everything.

58:00.141 --> 58:02.075
- God, you're so humble.
- That's right.

58:02.077 --> 58:04.644
Wait. I have a question.
If he's so awesome,

58:04.646 --> 58:07.483
- why did you fire him?
- [Scott laughs]

58:09.117 --> 58:12.151
Oh, was I supposed to ask
that in Chinese?

58:12.153 --> 58:14.954
- Oh, she's a pretty smart one, isn't she?
- [phone ringing]

58:14.956 --> 58:16.092
This is Scott.

58:17.059 --> 58:19.191
I told you to pick up
the daughter at 4 pm

58:19.193 --> 58:20.797
at the Bloomers. Come on.

58:22.231 --> 58:24.097
- Hey. Out.
- Taxi.

58:24.099 --> 58:25.902
[soft music]

58:26.802 --> 58:29.939
[plays the harmonica]

58:46.021 --> 58:48.588
- Can I have something with the crackers?
- Yes.

58:48.590 --> 58:51.927
- Ice cream?
- No. Do your homework.

58:52.695 --> 58:55.996
[Karen] <i>Hi. You've reached Karen,
your organizational specialist.</i>

58:55.998 --> 58:58.166
<i>Please, leave
your name and number.</i>

59:00.369 --> 59:04.972
[imitates the sound of a plane]

59:04.974 --> 59:07.943
[soft music continues]

59:29.764 --> 59:30.833
